These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-1::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: ship, motorbike, skateboard, bike, quad-bike
There are 5 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, 7up, juice, mirinda
 1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person driving the skateboard##7
 3. the person driving the ship and the person drinking mirinda have the same parity positions##9
 4. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
 5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 6. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
 7. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking water and the person drinking 7up##2
 8. the person driving the motorbike is not the person drinking juice##6
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |   4    |      5       |
| Pet     | motorbike | bike     | ship        | skateboard  | quad-bike          |
| Sport   | fanta  | water | mirinda | 7up | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-2::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: lavender, chestnut, mauve, emerald, light-blue
5 different games are played: backgammon, poker, billiard, go, scrabble
 1. the person playing poker is in an odd position##4
 2. the person playing billiard is somewhere between the person who likes mauve and the person playing go##7
 3. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
 4. the person playing billiard is somewhere between the person who likes mauve and the person playing go##7
 5. the person who likes lavender is the person playing backgammon##1
 6. the person who likes chestnut is in the middle##1
 7. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 8. the person who likes lavender and the person playing poker have different parity positions##9
 9. the person who likes lavender and the person playing billiard have different parity positions##9
10. the person playing backgammon is not to the right of the person who likes lavender##8
11. the person playing billiard is not to the right of the person who likes emerald##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |    3    |    4     |     5      |
| Food    | mauve  | lavender | chestnut  | light-blue | emerald     |
| Hobby   | scrabble | backgammon   | billiard | go  | poker |

