.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-3::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: weightlifting, handball, sailing, lacrosse, rugby
5 different pets are kept: cat, horse, pony, dog, snake
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the left of the owner of the horse##8
 2. the owner of the cat and the person who's sport is rugby have different parity positions##9
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is not the owner of the cat##6
 4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
 6. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
 7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
 9. the person who's sport is handball and the owner of the snake have different parity positions##9
10. the owner of the horse is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the person who's sport is lacrosse##7
11. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
12. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2     |    3     |       4       |       5        |
| Beverage   | rugby     | lacrosse     | sailing | handball | weightlifting          |
| Job        | pony | cat | horse | dog         | snake |

