.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-4::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: mystery, martial-arts, scientific, disaster, adventure
5 different games are played: scrabble, bridge, chess, backgammon, poker
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the left of the person playing scrabble##8
 2. the person playing poker is not to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
 3. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
 4. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere between the person watching disaster movies and the person playing chess##7
 5. the person playing scrabble and the person watching scientific movies have different parity positions##9
 6. the person playing bridge is not to the left of the person watching adventure movies##8
 7. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5
 8. the person watching mystery movies is not to the left of the person watching scientific movies##8
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
10. the person playing backgammon is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8
11. the person watching mystery movies is not to the left of the person playing scrabble##8
12. the person watching martial-arts movies is in the middle##1
13. the person playing poker is in the middle##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |    3     |     4      |    5     |
| Beverage   | scientific    | mystery  | martial-arts | adventure        | disaster |
| Pet        | chess | scrabble | poker    | bridge | backgammon      |

