 1. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
 2. the pall-mall-smoker is not the nigerian##6
 3. the nigerian and the ritmeester-smoker have different parity positions##9
 4. the oliveros-smoker is in the middle##1
 5. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the british##1
 6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the nigerian##1
 7. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
 8. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5
 9. the british is not the ritmeester-smoker##6
10. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
11. the indian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |    3     |      4      |   5   |
| Beverage    | dannemann  | pall-mall   | oliveros | ritmeester | siglo |
| Transport   | pakistani | indian | nigerian     | australian       | british   |

