.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-6::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: gardening, hiking, photography, baking, skydiving
There are 5 different favourite colors: light-blue, blue, aquamarine, orange, apricot
 1. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person who likes blue##1
 3. the person who likes apricot is not to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##8
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
 6. the person who's hobby is photography and the person who likes orange have the same parity positions##9
 7. the person who likes apricot is in the middle##1
 8. the person who likes light-blue is not the person who's hobby is baking##6
 9. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
10. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Movie-Genre   | gardening | baking    | hiking   | photography    | skydiving |
| Nationality   | light-blue | aquamarine | apricot | orange | blue    |

