.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-7::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: ivory, brown, apricot, red, pink
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: house, blues, reggae, pop, country
 1. the fan country and the person who likes apricot have different parity positions##9
 2. the fan pop is somewhere to the left of the fan country##5
 3. the fan house is not to the left of the fan pop##8
 4. the fan country is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ivory##5
 5. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the right of the person who likes pink##5
 6. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the fan blues##3
 7. the person who likes brown is not to the left of the fan blues##8
 8. the fan house and the person who likes ivory have the same parity positions##9
 9. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
10. the fan country is in an odd position##4
11. the fan blues is between the person who likes pink and the person who likes brown##2
12. the person who likes brown and the fan blues have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |    4     |     5     |
| Nationality   | pink       | red  | brown  | apricot   | ivory   |
| Sport         | pop | blues | country | reggae | house |

