 4. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 6. the person traveling to berlin and the person who likes orange have different parity positions##9
 7. the person who likes yellow is the person traveling to berlin##1
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
 9. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left or far right##3
