 3. the fan ambient is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##5
 4. the fan ambient is somewhere to the left of the fan gospel##5
 5. the fan gospel is somewhere between the fan electronic and the person traveling to san-francisco##7
 6. the person traveling to rome and the fan country have different parity positions##9
 7. the fan ambient is not to the left of the fan country##8
 8. the fan gospel is not the person traveling to hamburg##6
 9. the fan country is not to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##8
10. the fan gospel and the person traveling to rome have different parity positions##9
