 3. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5
 4. the cape-cod house is not the person driving the van##6
 5. the cape-cod house is somewhere between the person driving the van and the art-deco house##7
 6. the cape-cod house and the person driving the airplane have the same parity positions##9
 7. the cape-cod house is between the art-deco house and the gothic-revival house##2
 8. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
 9. the gothic-revival house is not the person driving the bus##6
10. the person driving the bus and the townhouse house have the same parity positions##9
11. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the art-deco house##1
12. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |    2     |   3    |  4   |   5    |
| Food   | gothic-revival | cape-cod  | art-deco | modern | townhouse |
